  panelId: recruit
  title: Recruiting
  body: 'Each unit costs <sprite="gem" index=0> Influence, paid on hire. Your army has limited <sprite="army" index=0> slots — at the cap you must disband someone first. Units act once per round and refresh when the round ends.'
